00558             const bool Sort(
00559                     const int (*cmp)(const T&, const T&)    
00560 
00561                     )
00562             {
00563                 bool b_Result = true;
00564                 if (GetCount() < 2)
00565                 {
00566                     b_Result = true;
00567                 }
00568                 else
00569                 {
00570                     // Get a reference element.
00571                     T t_Ref = RemoveTail();
00572 
00573                     // Dispatch elements in q_1 and q_2.
00574                     Queue<T> q_1(m_uiMaxCount), q_2(m_uiMaxCount);
00575                     while (! IsEmpty())
00576                     {
00577                         T t_Sort = RemoveTail();
00578                         if (cmp(t_Sort, t_Ref) > 0)
00579                         {
00580                             q_1.AddTail(t_Sort);
00581                         }
00582                         else
00583                         {
00584                             q_2.AddTail(t_Sort);
00585                         }
00586                     }
00587 
00588                     // Sort each list q_1 and q_2
00589                     if (q_1.Sort(cmp) && q_2.Sort(cmp))
00590                     {
00591                         // Eventually restore q_1...
00592                         b_Result = true;
00593                         for (   Iterator it_1 = q_1.GetIterator();
00594                                 q_1.IsValid(it_1);
00595                                 q_1.MoveNext(it_1))
00596                         {
00597                             if (! AddTail(q_1.GetAt(it_1)))
00598                             {
00599                                 b_Result = false;
00600                             }
00601                         }
00602                         // ... then the reference element...
00603                         if (! AddTail(t_Ref))
00604                         {
00605                             b_Result = false;
00606                         }
00607                         // ... and then q_2.
00608                         for (   Iterator it_2 = q_2.GetIterator();
00609                                 q_2.IsValid(it_2);
00610                                 q_2.MoveNext(it_2))
00611                         {
00612                             if (! AddTail(q_2.GetAt(it_2)))
00613                             {
00614                                 b_Result = false;
00615                             }
00616                         }
00617                     }
00618                 }
00619                 return b_Result;
00620             }
